### a. Reading files

**Definition:** *`with open(...)` ensures file is closed; `line.rstrip()` removes newline. In system design, file I/O maps to blob storage (S3, GCS), log files, config files. ETL pipelines read from files/object storage; append-only logs (WAL) use file semantics.*

**Syntax:**
```
